{"tid":2515605,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"盤點童年13款經典FC遊戲，絕對有你曾玩過的","createTime":"2021-05-04T06:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T10:53:06.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba3091aab96de5c5ab9032750ac547eae74acf0","tid":2515605,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:09:15.000Z","msg":"80後小的時候，電腦還沒有普及，唯一的電子娛樂就是紅白機，或者小霸王山寨機，插上卡帶就能玩遊戲，當時四合一的卡稍貴，但遊戲質量很好，多合一的便宜，但遊戲質量一般，那你還記得有哪些是你曾經玩過的遊戲呢？本期這十三款最經典的FC遊戲，絕對有你玩過的。<br />\n<br />\n  第一部《魂斗羅一代》<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0504%2F7b6574a1p00qsk66z009wc000ht00a1m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0504%252F7b6574a1p00qsk66z009wc000ht00a1m.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=0ca8aebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n最過癮的橫版射擊遊戲，八個章節，個個都有挑戰性和特色。<br />\n<br />\n  第二部《超級瑪麗》<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0504%2F67d9a1e7j00qsk66z0049c000zm00k2m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0504%252F67d9a1e7j00qsk66z0049c000zm00k2m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=5fc7d8c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n在全世界都很出名，裡面有很多隱藏內容，至今也沒有幾個人能完全解謎。<br />\n<br />\n  第三部《忍者龍劍3》<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0504%2Ff4072aa9j00qsk66z00cbc000zm00k2m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0504%252Ff4072aa9j00qsk66z00cbc000zm00k2m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=41687397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n忍者風格格鬥闖關遊戲，流程簡單，就是BOSS有點難打。<br />\n<br />\n  第四部《雙截龍3》<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0504%2F7fba93bcj00qsk66z0095c000zm00k2m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0504%252F7fba93bcj00qsk66z0095c000zm00k2m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=b96e104a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n打擊感最強的橫版格鬥遊戲，難度高，但戰鬥招式多樣化，還能放大招螺旋踢。<br />\n<br />\n  第五部《機械戰警》<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n當時算得上是大作，四合一卡帶才能玩到，能射擊，能格鬥，還能進入建築物。<br />\n<br />\n  第六部《松鼠大戰》<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0504%2F95d48f5fp00qsk66z0061c000ht00a1m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0504%252F95d48f5fp00qsk66z0061c000ht00a1m.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=6cca8b38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n快節奏的無敵松鼠，扔箱子，吃道具，快速奔跑，操作靈活。<br />\n<br />\n  第七部《冒險島3》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0504%2F0a05aa0cj00qsk66z0054c000zm00k2m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0504%252F0a05aa0cj00qsk66z0054c000zm00k2m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=55651391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n比超級瑪麗好玩，能丟錘子攻擊敵人，蹦起來加水果，後面還有各式各樣的麒麟。<br />\n<br />\n  第八部《忍者神龜格鬥》<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0504%2Fc3c97392j00qsk66z006hc000zm00k2m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0504%252Fc3c97392j00qsk66z006hc000zm00k2m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=3a6b3fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n簡稱&ldquo;神龜對打&rdquo;，大賴屬於禁用人物，二龜咬人也挺難纏，能觸發所有人物技能的全是大神。<br />\n<br />\n  第九部《忍者神龜3》<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0504%2Fc3c97392j00qsk66z006hc000zm00k2m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0504%252Fc3c97392j00qsk66z006hc000zm00k2m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=3a6b3fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n闖關格鬥很耐玩，每關都有特色，最終目的就是打敗BOSS，解救女神記者。<br />\n<br />\n  第十部《綠色兵團》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0504%2Fe42feb07j00qsk66z0051c000zm00k2m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0504%252Fe42feb07j00qsk66z0051c000zm00k2m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=8d585ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n全程一把小刀捅遍整個遊戲，途中還有火箭筒，一炮能幹掉一排人，玩著很有意思。<br />\n<br />\n  第十一部《赤色要塞》<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0504%2F8ff57fc3j00qsk66z00cvc000zm00k2m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0504%252F8ff57fc3j00qsk66z00cvc000zm00k2m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=734edfa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n一個小小吉普車，能把敵人基地打個翻天，不管是坦克、砲塔、飛機，小車就是大神的存在。<br />\n<br />\n  第十二部《古巴英雄》<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0504%2F587ea5f6j00qsk66z00e4c000zm00k2m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0504%252F587ea5f6j00qsk66z00e4c000zm00k2m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=3c1793b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n玩起來非常過癮，堪比上帝視角的魂斗羅，中途還能開坦克，想怎麼打就怎麼打。<br />\n<br />\n  第十三部《影子傳說》<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0504%2Fab9744f4j00qsk66z005cc000zm00k2m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0504%252Fab9744f4j00qsk66z005cc000zm00k2m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=9dae11d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n忍者循環救娘子，超級忍者彈跳，飛鏢連射，節奏很快，但沒弄明白那女的為啥總是被抓。"},{"pid":"cfbfe78b30a3f3fed854ab97d272f713186930c2","tid":2515605,"uid":116714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:45:08.000Z","msg":"除咗10-12，其他全部玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2883fa2fceea668f4d8d6135f514112e801b2ee0","tid":2515605,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隻隻都玩過但只有魂斗羅爆到機"}]}